comment: Leonard (SAS) cleanly knocks the ball away from Galloway (NYK).

Duncan (SAS) jumps vertically while contesting the driving layup by Thomas (NYK). He turns only after contact is initiated by Thomas.

LATR shows Parker (SAS) catches the ball while in the air, landing on his left foot. He then plants his right foot and reestablishes his left foot before passing the ball.
